\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{1}x^{n-1}\psi_{p}\left(x\right)dx=\frac{C_{p}}{n}\left[\frac{m_{p}^{n}-m_{l}^{n}}{m_{p}-m_{l}}-\frac{m_{u}^{n}-m_{p}^{n}}{m_{u}-m_{p}}\right]
\]

\end_inset

with the midpoint 
\begin_inset Formula $m_{p}$
\end_inset

 and the lower and upper midpoints 
\begin_inset Formula $m_{l}<m_{p}<m_{u}$
\end_inset

